{"tid":810712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國8月失業率持平於3.9%  經濟強勁擴張","createTime":"2018-09-08T07:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T04:59:38.000Z","uid":62257,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be4eee3f8f2b42e11a7f47881f34d5fc3d02e223","tid":810712,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:50:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4198509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4198509&d=VmjaXLCinPqSTEC05d1b1viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ab31fbba\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4198509</a><br />\n美國 8 月新增就業 20.1 萬人，顯示邁向夏季末，經濟依舊強勁擴張。<br />\n<br />\n接受 MarketWatch 調查的分析師平均預估，8 月新增就業為 20 萬人。<br />\n<br />\n8 月失業率為 3.9%，與 7 月持平。<br />\n<br />\n最重要的消息是工資上升。8 月平均每小時工資上升 10 美分，或 0.4%，至 27.16 美元。<br />\n<br />\n8 月平均每小時工資年率上升 2.9%，創 2009 年 6 月大衰退結束以來，最高水準。7 月年率為上升 2.7%。<br />\n7 月與 6 月新增就業合計下修 5 萬人。<br />\n<br />\n7 月新增就業由 15.7 萬人修正為 14.7 萬人。6 月新增就業由 24.8 萬人修正為 20.8 萬人。"},{"pid":"13c9e08c6a45246add5153b13411ed373da8ed05","tid":810712,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B8%E6%9C%88%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%873-9-%E8%96%AA%E8%B3%87%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E5%8A%A0%E5%BF%AB-235837003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.stock.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B8%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%258E%25873-9-%25E8%2596%25AA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%25A2%259E%25E9%2580%259F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BF%25AB-235837003.html&d=VmjaXLCinPqSTEC05d1b1viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=da3e9a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B8%E6%9C%88%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%8E%873-9-%E8%96%AA%E8%B3%87%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E5%8A%A0%E5%BF%AB-235837003.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018/09/08 07:58 中央社 中央社 <br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓2018年9月7日綜合外電報導）美國政府今天公布報告指出，8月美國勞工平均時薪出現近10年來最大增幅，並且出現罕見的夏末招聘熱潮，看不出就業巿場可能有降溫跡象。<br />\n<br />\n報告顯示，營造、運輸、批發貿易、金融和醫療保健等產業就業呈現增長，這項出人意表的成長情況給美國總統川普打了一劑強心針。川普本週遭遇幕僚積極尋求減損他威信的報導所擾。<br />\n<br />\n美國8月失業率穩定維持在已然低檔的3.9%，增加20萬1000個工作機會。<br />\n<br />\n在11月關鍵選舉之前，本週為薪資成長疲軟報導所苦的白宮，勢必將歡迎平均時薪年增2.9%的消息。這是2009年6月以來最大增幅，並且跟消費者通膨走勢一致。<br />\n<br />\n薪資強勁增長也將使外界更堅定預期美國聯邦準備理事會（Fed）今年會繼續升息腳步，以抑制通膨。（譯者：何宏儒）"},{"pid":"571848c68ffbf1b72d56029283a391b92d692293","tid":810712,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1fdcdcaee1e7ddb5e8f2512f52d52c4206502f","tid":810712,"uid":112583,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:00:04.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬出黎認屎認屁未？"},{"pid":"914d0241f540dd791907f9c9a18f4d572a57e82b","tid":810712,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554f1ec24996138e8cf0c08ee069ce04fefe25b2","tid":810712,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0bbb5b52e51afdad88d19eeb691101846deb9c","tid":810712,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d1fdcdcaee1e7ddb5e8f2512f52d52c4206502f","tid":810712,"uid":112583,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:00:04.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬出黎認屎認屁未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"酸死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb6b4548a799d2866309f478d4b8909bb96e955","tid":810712,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99825a81381e5aeca73362598897a81e88a58b05","tid":810712,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d1fdcdcaee