ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1fdcdcaee1e7ddb5e8f2512f52d52c4206502f","tid":810712,"uid":112583,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:00:04.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬出黎認屎認屁未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T22:28:26.000Z","msg":"以下是美國勞工統計局提供的就業數據：<br />\n<br />\n2014年(奧巴馬)：平均每月新增258250個就業崗位，當年共增加3099000個就業崗位。<br />\n<br />\n2015年(奧巴馬)：平均每月增加221417個就業崗位，當年共增加2657000個就業崗位。<br />\n<br />\n2016年(奧巴馬)：平均每月新增176333個就業崗位，當年共增加2116000個就業崗位。<br />\n<br />\n2017年(特朗普)：平均每月增加170500個工作崗位，當年共增加2046000個就業崗位。<br />\n<br />\n2018年(特朗普)：迄今平均每月增加20.8萬個工作崗位，當年共增加2046000個就業崗位。"},{"pid":"926a3c15ba994e9e329ee0d47da15501340af707","tid":810712,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"加息了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c1d7c33edb5216404a39c9ce4ae2829665584a","tid":810712,"uid":185126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"當初投trump就係想睇到咁嘅強勢美國<br />\n好難諗佢地點解下一屆會唔投返trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}